## Upload User Picture

Upload and update user's profile picture on Zoom via user ID.

> Definition

```text
POST <%= config[:api_host] %>user/uploadpicture
```

> Example Request

```shell
$ curl <%= config[:api_host] %>user/updatepassword \
    -d api_key=<%= config[:ex_api_key] %> \
    -d api_secret=<%= config[:ex_api_secret] %> \
    -d id=<%= config[:ex_uuid] %> \
    -d pic_file="https://domain.com/path/to/pic.jpg"
```

```javascript
<%= config[:ex_node_init] %>

var user = {
    id : "<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>",
    pic_file: "https://domain.com/path/to/pic.jpg"
}

Zoom.user.updatePicture(user, <%= config[:ex_node_res] %>);
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "id": "<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>",
  "updated_at": "2013-09-02T12:00:00Z"
}
```

Arguments | &nbsp;
--- | ---
id **required** | User id.
pic_file **required** | User picture file, must be a jpg/jpeg file.